Android NDK Requirement For 16 KB Support
-----------------------------------------

Do **not** use the stable SDK-manager NDK r25 package for this 16 KB build.

Why:

- this repo still depends on the older NDK layout and was not moved to NDK 29
- stable NDK `25.1.8937393` produced a 4 KB `libc++_shared.so`
- for 16 KB support on this old NDK line, the build needed an Android CI canary
  NDK package that already contains a 16 KB-aligned `libc++_shared.so`

Use this Android CI build:

- Branch:
  `aosp-ndk-r25-release`
- Build:
  `12161346`
- Artifact:
  `android-ndk-12161346-darwin-x86_64.zip`
- Extracted folder name:
  `android-ndk-r25d-canary`

The Android CI page used for this was:

`https://ci.android.com/builds/branches/aosp-ndk-r25-release/grid?head=12161346&tail=12161346&legacy=1`

Manual download process:

1. Open the CI page above.
2. Open the `darwin_mac` target for build `12161346`.
3. Download artifact `android-ndk-12161346-darwin-x86_64.zip`.
4. Unzip it.
5. Move the extracted `android-ndk-r25d-canary` folder to a stable local path.

Recommended stable install path:

`$HOME/Library/Android/ndk/android-ndk-r25d-canary`

Example:

```sh
mkdir -p "$HOME/Library/Android/ndk"
mv android-ndk-r25d-canary "$HOME/Library/Android/ndk/"
```

Build Variant
-------------

This was the Android package variant rebuilt successfully:

`--enable-lame --enable-opus --enable-gpl --enable-rubberband --disable-lib-x264 --disable-lib-x265 --disable-lib-xvidcore --disable-lib-libvidstab`

Because this checkout had already been built on another machine/path before,
the successful rebuild also forced regeneration of the enabled dependency
outputs:

`--rebuild-cpu-features --rebuild-lame --rebuild-libiconv --rebuild-libsndfile --rebuild-libsamplerate --rebuild-opus --rebuild-rubberband`

Normal Build Command
--------------------

Run from the repo root.

Replace the NDK path below if you install it somewhere else.

```sh
export ANDROID_SDK_ROOT="$HOME/Library/Android/sdk"
export ANDROID_HOME="$HOME/Library/Android/sdk"
export ANDROID_NDK_ROOT="$HOME/Library/Android/ndk/android-ndk-r25d-canary"
export ANDROID_NDK="$HOME/Library/Android/ndk/android-ndk-r25d-canary"
export JAVA_HOME="/opt/homebrew/opt/openjdk@17/libexec/openjdk.jdk/Contents/Home"
export PATH="$HOME/Library/Android/sdk/cmake/3.22.1/bin:/opt/homebrew/opt/openjdk@17/bin:/opt/homebrew/opt/libtool/libexec/gnubin:/opt/homebrew/bin:$PATH"

./android.sh \
  --rebuild-cpu-features \
  --rebuild-lame \
  --rebuild-libiconv \
  --rebuild-libsndfile \
  --rebuild-libsamplerate \
  --rebuild-opus \
  --rebuild-rubberband \
  --enable-lame \
  --enable-opus \
  --enable-gpl \
  --enable-rubberband \
  --disable-lib-x264 \
  --disable-lib-x265 \
  --disable-lib-xvidcore \
  --disable-lib-libvidstab
```

